verses.roman:
ei-mate sanātana vṛndāvane āilā
pāche āsi' rūpa-gosāñi tāṅhāre mililā

synonyms: ei-mate—in this way; sanātana—Sanātana Gosvāmī; vṛndāvane āilā—came to Vṛndāvana; pāche āsi'-coming after; rūpa-gosāñi—Śrīla Rūpa Gosvāmī; tāṅhāre—him; mililā—met.
translation: In this way Sanātana Gosvāmī reached Vṛndāvana. Later Rūpa Gosvāmī came and met him.
